Retrieve the names of all available datasets

Source: R/SpecimenClient-wrapper.r
specimen_dwca_get_data_set_names.Rd

This is a wrapper function for dwca_get_data_set_names from class nbaR.SpecimenClient.

specimen_dwca_get_data_set_names(returnType = "data.frame", ...)

Arguments

returnType

Either 'list' or 'data.frame', defaults to 'data.frame'
...

additional parameters passed to dwca_get_data_set_names from class nbaR.SpecimenClient

Value

scalar

Details

Individual datasets can then be downloaded with /dwca/getDataSet/dataset
